>
  <p class="flex flex-col gap-1">
    <Icon name="system-uicons:cubes" class="text-neutral-400 text-6xl" />
    <span
      >Developed with <a
        href="https://astro.build"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="border-b-2 border-b-neutral-800 hover:border-b-transparent text-neutral-700 text-semibold hover:text-neutral-500 transition-all duration-150"
        >Astro</a
      >.</span
    >
    <span>
      Heavily inspired by <a
        class="border-b-2 border-b-neutral-800 hover:border-b-transparent text-neutral-700 text-semibold hover:text-neutral-500 transition-all duration-150"
        href="https://frosti.saroprock.com"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank">Frosti Theme</a
      >, developed by <a
        class="border-b-2 border-b-neutral-800 hover:border-b-transparent text-neutral-700 text-semibold hover:text-neutral-500 transition-all duration-150"
        href="https://github.com/EveSunMaple"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank">SunMapple</a
      >
    </span>
    <span>
