    </span>
  </p>
  <p class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-extrabold text-md uppercase">
    Links
    <span class="flex gap-1 text-neutral-700">
      <a
        href="https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/110005305"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        ><Icon name="fa6-brands:pixiv" class="w-[28px] h-[28px]" /></a
      >
      <a
        href="https://x.com/_kiseki_miracle"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        ><Icon name="fa6-brands:x-twitter" class="w-[28px] h-[28px]" /></a
      >
      <a
        href="https://github.com/KisekiMiracle"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        ><Icon name="fa6-brands:github" class="w-[28px] h-[28px]" /></a
      >
      <a
        href="https://vgen.co/KisekiMiracle"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
